metadata.name: "When Two Cults Collide" by KasparK
metadata.description:
"When it comes to the pursuit of knowledge and the unknown, there is no topic that is off limits for the Technocult. There have been massive efforts to uncover the secrets of the Occult and thus the gates of unimaginable cosmic horrors were recently unveiled.

Although the psyche of one can get destroyed by thoughts of the Elder Gods and their disciples, the bravest have found a passage beyond the veil and made contact with  the Demon Death Cult. The cults have joined forces and only time will tell what 
they can provide one another.

One is for sure - The metaverse will never be the same."

---

Artwork by KasparK - commissioned by Demon Death Cult
